Description_lang: Cleaves players in a half-circle in front of him, inflicting $s2 Physical damage and increasing damage taken by subsequent Soulrending Scythes by $s3%. This effect stacks.Additionally, whenever a player is hit by Soulrending Scythe, they will release a Rent Soul which will move towards a player, detonating on the first player it touches.
AuraDescription_lang: Damage taken from Soulrending Scythe increased by $s3%.
